dc_description_s: This data layer represents recreation locations for Polk County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase “Polk_Recreation_2016.gdb”. The features included in this geodatabase are 'BoatAccess' and 'Recreation'.[Enhanced 911 and general mapping purposes.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: https://www.polkcountywi.gov/government/divisions_and_departments/environmental_services_division/land_information/gis_data_portal.php
